# PoolMaster — Terraform Variables
#
# DEPRECATED: Use per-environment tfvars instead:
#   cp envs/qa.tfvars.example envs/qa.tfvars
#   cp envs/staging.tfvars.example envs/staging.tfvars
#   cp envs/prod.tfvars.example envs/prod.tfvars
#
# Then deploy with:
#   terraform init -backend-config=envs/qa.backend.hcl
#   terraform apply -var-file=envs/qa.tfvars
#
# See plans/16-aws-deployment.md for full instructions.
